  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Investigators aim to evaluate the SEPSIS 3 criterion for &quot;sepsis&quot; and &quot;septic shock&quot; in a
      prospective manner.

      Investigators will evaluate qSOFA performances and other SEPSIS 3 criterion in a population
      of emergency patients with infection
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
